# =================================================================
# Ledom Layouter - Project Ignore Configuration
# Designed for Version v1.3.0 | AI Solutions Architect
# =================================================================

### --- Python Core ---
# 自动生成的字节码缓存，剔除冗余
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

### --- Environment & Virtual Environments ---
# 隔离开发环境，不提交至仓库
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
bin/
lib/
include/
share/

### --- Streamlit & Web Internal ---
# 隐藏 Streamlit 运行时的本地配置与凭证
.streamlit/config.toml
.streamlit/secrets.toml

### --- Application Output (Redundant Files) ---
# 剔除运行期间生成的临时 Word 文档
Ledom_Layouter_*.docx
*.tmp
*.log

### --- OS Metadata ---
# 剔除操作系统生成的索引文件
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

### --- Development Tools ---
# 隐藏 IDE 局部的特定配置
.vscode/
.idea/
.RooCode/
.clinerules